title: Queen Live killers in Paris 1979
description:
27.02.1979 Video recording Short snippet from the &#039;Paris 1979&#039; QTV concert video is from this concert (Freddie saying goodbye to the audience). More footage might be in the band&#039;s archives.
28.02.1979 Some songs appear in the &#039;Paris 1979&#039; QTV concert video (QTV), some are in the &#039;Champions&#039; documentary (US). This is what the research of some collectors revealed: Let Me Entertain You (US), Somebody To Love (QTV), If You Can&#039;t Beat Them (QTV), Get Down Make Love (US - middle section only), Now I&#039;m Here (US - a few bits), Bohemian Rhapsody (QTV), Tie Your Mother Down (QTV/US), Sheer Heart Attack (QTV/US), We Will Rock You (US).
01.03.1979 Most songs appear in the &#039;Paris 1979&#039; QTV concert video (QTV), a few are in the &#039;Champions&#039; documentary (US).
